01:09:11,385 --> 01:09:14,218
- Present.

701
01:09:15,589 --> 01:09:19,252
"There was so much to learn
and there was such little time."

702
01:09:20,094 --> 01:09:21,220
"24 hours without tiring..."

703
01:09:22,062 --> 01:09:26,726
"Your fingers would speak to me."

704
01:09:27,301 --> 01:09:30,634
Whether life starts from
the womb or from the earth...

705
01:09:31,605 --> 01:09:37,566
its journey starts from darkness
and ends in darkness.

706
01:09:39,013 --> 01:09:42,471
One day we will all have to pass
through this darkness...

707
01:09:42,950 --> 01:09:49,514
and reach into the light.

708
01:09:49,923 --> 01:09:53,222
"One day, we all have to go through
the darkness, to... light..."

709
01:09:53,994 --> 01:09:56,258
"New doors opened up for me..."

710
01:09:56,997 --> 01:10:01,491
"new friends, new stories,
new poetry..."

711
01:10:02,670 --> 01:10:04,433
"a new way of looking at the world"

712
01:10:05,205 --> 01:10:08,003
"what you see is what you dream'

713
01:10:09,877 --> 01:10:13,040
No. She, she... she disagrees
with the poet

714
01:10:14,214 --> 01:10:17,843
Eyes don't see dreams
but the mind does.

715
01:10:18,652 --> 01:10:24,386
I can't see with my eyes,
yet I dream.

716
01:10:24,958 --> 01:10:29,622
Our dream is that one-day
I would graduate.

717
01:10:41,675 --> 01:10:45,372
Are you ready?

718
01:10:45,579 --> 01:10:46,637
Ready...

719
01:10:48,182 --> 01:10:50,480
Tree...
- Tree...

720
01:10:51,418 --> 01:10:53,750
Burr...
- Butterfly...

721
01:10:54,354 --> 01:10:56,481
Bir...
- Bird...

722
01:10:57,024 --> 01:10:58,821
Fish...
- Fish...

723
01:11:00,027 --> 01:11:01,654
Bee...
- Bee...

724
01:11:09,837 --> 01:11:14,501
"The best years of my life..."

725
01:11:15,409 --> 01:11:17,536
"memories of which
bring joy even today"

726
01:11:32,092 --> 01:11:33,525
It's ok...

727
01:11:34,928 --> 01:11:35,860
It's all right!

728
01:11:43,203 --> 01:11:44,864
What? Tickly?

729
01:11:56,216 --> 01:12:00,209
It's not going to snow.
Please concentrate on your studies

730
01:12:01,588 --> 01:12:05,217
No, no... you wont need the
umbrella at all, concentrate.

731
01:12:19,306 --> 01:12:21,399
Give me the umbrella.
Hey stop it...

732
01:12:21,608 --> 01:12:22,575
Give me the umbrella...

733
01:12:22,776 --> 01:12:23,743
Give me the umbrella...
give... me... The umbrella

734
01:12:57,978 --> 01:12:59,104
"Can't you see"?

735
01:12:59,947 --> 01:13:00,606
I'm sorry sir

736
01:13:02,983 --> 01:13:07,784
Hey... no... no. No.
It's alright... it's alright.

737
01:13:08,121 --> 01:13:10,282
No, no...

738
01:13:10,891 --> 01:13:14,827
you are too slow!
How will you pass?

739
01:13:16,163 --> 01:13:16,959
You'll try?

740
01:13:18,031 --> 01:13:18,963
Let's watch it

